casebody.data:
In the Matter of Nathaniel K. Charny (Admitted as Nathaniel Kires Charny), a Suspended Attorney.

[— NYS2d —]

—This Court’s order entered on April 15, 1999 (257 AD2d 18) amended by referring this matter to the Departmental Disciplinary Committee to designate a Hearing Panel to conduct a hearing, as indicated. No opinion. Concur — Williams, J. P., Mazzarelli, Ellerin, Rubin and Saxe, JJ.
